      "properties": {"Node name for S&R": "Note"},
      "widgets_values": [
        "LIP-SYNC POST-FX (after LatentSync)\n=========================================\n\nPIPELINE:\n  1. CodeFormer (gentle — 0.65 weight, less than Sonic pack)\n     LatentSync already produces cleaner mouths than Sonic,\n     so CodeFormer doesn't need to work as hard.\n  2. RIFE (25fps → 50fps)\n  3. Deflicker\n  4. LUT\n  5. 4x UltraSharp + pixel cap to 2048\n  6. Blend\n  7. Film grain\n  8. Save H.264 CRF 16 @ 50fps with original audio preserved\n\nWHY CODEFORMER WEIGHT 0.65 (vs 0.7 in Sonic pack)?\n  LatentSync's mouth rendering is cleaner than Sonic's, so\n  CodeFormer only needs light cleanup. Higher weight (0.85+)\n  would over-smooth the singer's natural skin texture."
      ],
